There were 2 ornaments of gold...It was rolled up in a [bundle?] but when opened it was a long strip of gold, about, about 1/4 of an inch in width, with a kind of crook at the end to fasten with. It was a very large piece and weighed about the weight of 2 guineas; if I recollect right there were 2 similar pieces."
